            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-e6dc5a04-2d34-4618-9794-0ae35982cdcd">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Chamberlain)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e6dc5a04-2d34-4618-9794-0ae35982cdcd" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1937-06-14/debates/1271eb01-d883-45d4-942d-61059fd98237/PensionsAndInsuranceSchemes#contribution-e6dc5a04-2d34-4618-9794-0ae35982cdcd">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The facts as regards the scope of the social insurance schemes are, I think, already well known, and, as the hon. Member is aware, a number of extensions have recently been made. I do not think that the appointment of a Royal Commission would serve any useful purpose.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-e6dc5a04-2d34-4618-9794-0ae35982cdcd" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1937-06-14/debates/1271eb01-d883-45d4-942d-61059fd98237/PensionsAndInsuranceSchemes#contribution-e6dc5a04-2d34-4618-9794-0ae35982cdcd">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





